{"tid":2003298,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城大校長唔香港再出發只係因為台灣有《兩岸條例》","createTime":"2020-05-05T16:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T17:29:14.000Z","uid":27986,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"31f68c7c20cb32a1aceb2d3cdcf8ca49055d95b3","tid":2003298,"uid":27986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/328/5dce2440ee140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F328%2F5dce2440ee140.jpg&h=6ca43aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返搞侵侵個東方衛視記者張經義<br />\n佢係台灣人，但做共狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200417/WOKNA5SSVJN4SRQVBL5YTB2KUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200417%2FWOKNA5SSVJN4SRQVBL5YTB2KUM%2F&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRHJTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=1431eadc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200417%2FWOKNA5SSVJN4SRQVBL5YTB2KUM%2F&h=ad5504b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200417/WOKNA5SSVJN4SRQVBL5YTB2KUM/</a><br />\n<br />\n//陸委會指出，陸方黨務、政務系統所屬事業單位，屬《兩岸條例》第33條第2項公告禁止任職黨政軍組織，規定指出台灣人民不得擔任公告禁止中國大陸黨務、軍事、行政或具政治性機關(構)、團體職務或為其成員；違反規定依法處台幣10萬以上50萬元以下罰鍰。<br />\n <br />\n陸委會說，東方衛視是上海東方娛樂傳媒所屬衛星頻道，隸屬陸方政務系統上海市國有資產監督管理委員會全額出資上海文化廣播影視集團；受黨務系統中共上海市委宣傳部所屬事業單位（上海廣播電視台）指揮監督。股權隸屬及業務監督關係，足以認定東方衛視為陸方黨務、政務系統所屬事業單位，自屬《兩岸條例》公告禁止任職黨政軍組織。//<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">城大校長郭位作為台灣人<br />\n又係台灣中研院士<br />\n實際投共咪得<br />\n退休仲要返台灣<br />\n點會俾挖個窿俾自己踩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2f75621c1f34373bbd8012185eeb2c8b20ff9b","tid":2003298,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27513d9295f32ae17761694154c50dbdbd24b2d","tid":2003298,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor